---
import { site } from "../data/site";
---

<section
  id="about"
  class="relative isolate scroll-mt-24 overflow-hidden text-ink-900"
  style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f5f4f1 0%, #faf9f6 100%);"
>
  <!-- top transition from dark -->
  <div
    class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-0 -top-px h-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-ink-950 to-transparent"
    aria-hidden="true"
  ></div>

  <!-- bottom transition back to dark -->
  <div
    class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-0 -bottom-px h-32 bg-gradient-to-t from-ink-950 to-transparent"
    aria-hidden="true"
  ></div>

  <!-- subtle warm wash -->
  <div
    class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 -z-10 opacity-40"
    style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 50% at 50% 0%, rgba(167,139,250,0.08), transparent 60%);"
    aria-hidden="true"
  ></div>

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-start">
      <div class="md:col-span-5 md:sticky md:top-32">
        <p class="reveal mb-4 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-ink-500">
          Why we exist
        </p>
        <h2 class="reveal display text-5xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-medium">
          <span class="text-gradient-ink">Built for</span><br />
          <span class="font-serif italic text-gradient-violet">founders who actually do</span><br />
          <span class="text-gradient-ink">the work.</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-7 space-y-7 text-[17px] text-ink-800 leading-relaxed">
        <p class="reveal">
          The agency world is broken. Founders pay <span class="text-ink-900 font-medium">$10,000 a month</span> for slide decks, status calls, and accounts that mysteriously underperform - then get told they need a longer contract to "see results."
        </p>
        <p class="reveal">
          We started Allaia because we got tired of watching good operators with great offers get bled out by retainers they could not justify. So we built the opposite.
        </p>
        <p class="reveal font-serif italic text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-gradient-violet leading-snug">
          One operator on your account. AI doing the leverage. Real numbers in real dashboards. WhatsApp instead of weekly status calls.
        </p>
        <p class="reveal">
          We're a small, remote-first studio with people on the ground in {site.markets.join(", ")}. We take a handful of clients per quarter on purpose - because attention is the actual product, not headcount.
        </p>

        <!-- mini stats row -->
        <div class="reveal grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 pt-8">
          {[
            { v: "1 operator", l: "per account" },
            { v: "0 retainers", l: "longer than 3 mo" },
            { v: "<4h", l: "WhatsApp reply" },
          ].map((m) => (
            <div class="surface-warm rounded-2xl p-4">
              <div class="font-serif italic text-xl sm:text-2xl text-gradient-violet">
                {m.v}
              </div>
              <div class="mt-1 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-ink-500">
                {m.l}
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
